{
  "stem": "19218.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And she died with-- she had all her loved ones there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] All the kids were there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "My best friends were there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "[CRYING] [PAUSES FOR 10 SECONDS] [SIGHS] Of course, according to our traditions, she-- they did not perform any autopsies on her.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And I waited until [SIGHS] the funeral home came to take her away.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And we left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "It was tough for all of us to accept it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "She was the greatest mother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "She was the greatest grandmother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Of course, she was a lover, a wife, a partner.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "[SIGHS] She was a friend to everyone.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "If she touched someone, I mean, there wasn't a person in this world which wouldn't like her.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Of course, we all miss her terribly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "[SIGHS] For the next year, according to our tradition, we have to go to services.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And we finally had an unveiling, which was June 30 of this year, on a Sunday.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And we put a marker on her grave.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And we had quite a few people at the unveiling.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] And knowing I-- I just had to say a few words in there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "I knew it was going to be very hard.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "But I decided to write something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "I never knew I had it in me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "But 5:30 that morning, I couldn't sleep.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "I got up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And I put together something, which I tried to read.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And I did read it at the unveiling.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "I was asked to read this and I gladly will, if I can.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "In her honor.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "In her tribute.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 10 SECONDS] [SIGHS] June 30, 1996, in memory to my beloved wife, Esther.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] If I could reverse time, you would forever be mine.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "If I could hold the tide, you would always be by my side.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
